00:43:20.648 --> 00:43:26.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Reading his Word
gives me the power.

00:43:26.053 --> 00:43:32.826 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When storms in life come,
he’s my strong Tower.

00:43:32.826 --> 00:43:44.338 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
