The new world is in sight.

00:44:09.296 --> 00:44:12.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘Just keep on holding tight.

00:44:12.700 --> 00:44:19.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘I’ll help you win this fight—
Fight.

00:44:19.640 --> 00:44:31.151 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
